    Class: QuantityValue

    used to record a measurement

    URI: mixs.vocab:QuantityValue

    Slots

    Name Cardinality and Range Description Inheritance
    has unit 0..1
    NONE    		 Example "m" direct
    has numeric value 0..1
    xsd:double    		 direct
    has raw value 0..1
    NONE    		 direct
